{"prompt": "Generate a website for a podcasting network. The website should be minimalist and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Crimson Sound Network</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f8f8f8;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #c0392b; /* Brand red */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 960px;\n            margin: 40px auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 50px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .section h2 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            color: #c0392b; /* Brand red */\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #e74c3c; /* Lighter red for accent */\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            display: inline-block;\n        }\n        .podcast-list {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n        .podcast-item {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 25px;\n            width: 280px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n        .podcast-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n        .podcast-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #c0392b; /* Brand red */\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n        .podcast-item p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n        .podcast-item a {\n            display: inline-block;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            color: #c0392b; /* Brand red */\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .podcast-item a:hover {\n            color: #e74c3c; /* Lighter red */\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        footer a {\n            color: #c0392b; /* Brand red */\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #e74c3c; /* Lighter red */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #c0392b; /* Brand red */\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Crimson Sound Network</h1>\n        <p>Where compelling stories find their voice.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <main class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Our Featured Podcasts</h2>\n            <div class=\"podcast-list\">\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <h3>The Daily Chronicle</h3>\n                    <p>Your essential daily news briefing, delivered with clarity and depth. Stay informed with concise analysis of current events.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\">Listen Now</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <h3>Tech Forward</h3>\n                    <p>Exploring the latest in technology, innovation, and digital culture. Join us as we discuss the future of tech.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\">Listen Now</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"podcast-item\">\n                    <h3>Crimson Tales</h3>\n                    <p>Immersive audio dramas and captivating fictional narratives. Get lost in worlds of imagination.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\">Listen Now</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">View All Podcasts</a>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"section\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>Crimson Sound Network is dedicated to producing high-quality, engaging audio content across a variety of genres. We believe in the power of sound to inform, entertain, and inspire.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Learn More</a>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Crimson Sound Network. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Contact us at: <a href=\"mailto:info@crimsonsound.com\">info@crimsonsound.com</a></p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}